    "valueProposition": "Automated compliance solutions transform compliance from a reactive overhead into a proactive, measurable business asset. By eliminating manual inefficiencies, reducing risk exposure, and accelerating market access, a ~$15,000/year investment in robust compliance software can yield significant returns. It breaks even on time savings alone in approximately 75 working days, delivering an ROI of 3x or more, not including the exponential value of mitigating catastrophic regulatory failures or product launch delays. This investment ensures 'knowing' replaces the costly gamble of 'not knowing', safeguarding revenue and reputation."
