    "User prompt: core narrative ('Compliance is a measurable business asset')",
    "User prompt: 'Compliance Velocity Scorecard' name",
    "B2B lead generation best practices (instant value, compelling data)"
  ],
  "reasoning": "The 'Compliance Velocity vs. Industry Peers' metric is the most compelling primary hook because it directly aligns with the 'Compliance Velocity Scorecard' name, immediately establishing relevance. It addresses a profound unknown for validation/quality professionals: how their operational efficiency in compliance stacks up against competitors. This hook taps into both fear (of being outpaced, losing competitive advantage) and aspiration (desire to be an industry leader, make smart decisions). Presenting this data allows professionals to look smart to their boss by quantifying a strategic aspect of compliance, moving it from a perceived overhead to a measurable business asset. The inherent curiosity and competitive nature of the industry make this insight highly shareable, fueling organic lead generation. It provides instant, compelling value by offering a benchmark previously unavailable, creating a clear path for further engagement to address identified gaps."
